Transcription.Text: "No, thank you, Clive. I shall be able to manage. Afterwards he drove me back to Bletcham and we parted like old friends. He suggested another meeting, but I refused; the boat was such an attraction that I was afraid, if he came near it again, that I should never see the last of him.
